<br/>
<b><big><a name="Ublas Linkage" id="Ublas Linkage">Ublas Linkage</a></big></b>
<br/>
The <code><font color="blue">mat2cpp.hpp</font></code> contains 
the following include commands:
<code><font color='blue'><pre style='display:inline'> 
	# include &lt;boost/numeric/ublas/matrix.hpp&gt;
	# include &lt;boost/numeric/ublas/matrix_proxy.hpp&gt;
</pre></font></code>

In addition, it links the following 
<code><font color="blue">ublas</font></code> identifiers to the <code><font color="blue">mat2cpp</font></code> namespace:
<code><font color="blue">matrix</font></code>, <code><font color="blue">zero_matrix</font></code>, <code><font color="blue">scalar_matrix</font></code>,
<code><font color="blue">slice</font></code>, <code><font color="blue">matrix_slice</font></code>.
It also defines <code><font color="blue">matrix_slice_double</font></code> using
<code><font color='blue'><pre style='display:inline'> 
	typedef matrix_slice&lt; matrix&lt;double&gt; &gt;  matrix_slice_double;
</pre></font></code>


<br/>
<br/>
